Hey! We're agency which represent Betway Sport Betting App, licensed in the UK,Ireland, Ontario, Spain, Mexico, Germany. We run campaigns for this brand in Meta, Google, Snapchat and multiple In-App ad networks. We provide valid sports betting licenses. I came across you ad platform and would like to know if we can run our offers after we provide licenses to your team.

Hey! Thanks for reaching out. NewsBreak is a US-only traffic source, and we currently do not support advertising for sports betting apps, even with valid licenses. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
You're welcome! If you have any other questions or need assistance with anything else, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
